---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const pageTitle = "Aditya Varshney";
---

<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <div class="gif">
    <img width="300" height="259" alt="RaccoonSpaceGif" src="/space.webp" />
  </div>
  <h1>Aditya</h1>
  <span class="badge">A Full Stack Web Developer</span>
  <h2>About</h2>
  <p>
    I'm Aditya Varshney, a full-stack web developer deeply passionate about
    crafting captivating user experiences through animations and micro
    interactions. With a solid foundation in both front-end and back-end
    technologies, I specialize in building robust web applications that
    seamlessly marry aesthetics with functionality. As a contributor at
    SuperTeam, I have the privilege of collaborating on cutting-edge projects,
    where I contribute my expertise to push the boundaries of web development. I
    thrive in dynamic environments, constantly seeking out opportunities for
    growth and innovation. Beyond coding, I'm an avid learner, always exploring
    emerging technologies and sharing knowledge within the developer community.
    Whether it's experimenting with animation techniques, staying abreast of
    UX/UI trends, or contributing to open-source projects, I am dedicated to
    excellence and driven by a relentless pursuit of creating remarkable digital
    experiences.
  </p>

  <div class="center">
    <a href="/works/">
      <button class="btn">My portfolio</button>
    </a>
  </div>
  <h2>Skills</h2>
  <div class="skills center">
    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="TypeScript"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/typescript/typescript-original.svg"
    />
    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="React"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/react/react-original.svg"
    />
    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="Next.js"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/nextjs/nextjs-original.svg"
    />
    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="Node.js"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/nodejs/nodejs-original.svg"
    />
    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="MongoDB"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/mongodb/mongodb-original.svg"
    />
    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="PostgreSQL"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/postgresql/postgresql-original.svg"
    />
    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="Tailwind CSS"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/tailwindcss/tailwindcss-original.svg"
    />
    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="CSS"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/css3/css3-original.svg"
    />
    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="HTML"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/html5/html5-original.svg"
    />
    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="JavaScript"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/javascript/javascript-original.svg"
    />
    <img
      class="skills__img"
      width="46"
      height="46"
      alt="Git"
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/git/git-original.svg"
    />
  </div>

  <h2>Interests</h2>
  <h2>Interests</h2>
  <p>
    As a passionate web developer, I thrive on exploring new technologies and
    frameworks to enhance my skills. I'm particularly interested in front-end
    development, where I enjoy creating engaging user interfaces and
    implementing intricate animations. Additionally, I have a keen interest in
    backend technologies, especially in building scalable and efficient
    server-side solutions. Outside of coding, I enjoy staying updated on the
    latest industry trends, participating in tech meetups, and contributing to
    open-source projects. I also find joy in exploring nature, reading, and
    spending quality time with friends and family.
  </p>
</Layout>
